---
title: Lemon & Honey-Mustard Chicken with Roasted Pumpkin Wedges & Creamy Rainbow Slaw
description: The classic combination of honey and mustard never goes amiss. We love the way these flavours caramelise in
the pan. The chicken breast packs a fantastic flavour, remains moist as it cooks and complements the serving of
delicious sweet roasted pumpkin and creamy slaw.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemon-honey-mustard-chicken-7924205f.jpg
